headline.main: CHINA CLAIMS ROUT OF ENEMY IN SOUTH; Reports Japanese in Flight Toward Canton After a 5-Day Battle in Waichow Region DIVISION SAID TO DESERT Nanking Puppet Force Comes Over With Its General, Chungking Declares

lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, Jan. 31 (AP) -- Japanese troops are in full retreat toward Canton tonight after being defeated in a five-day battle with Chinese forces east of the city, a Chinese communique said tonight.
abstract: Jap troops reptd retreating toward Canton after 5-day battle, Waichow area
